metadata.name: BeetsDAO Founder's Pass #0001/1000
metadata.description:
The Founder's Pass grants holders quarterly art and utility for BeetsDAO drops, partners and IRL & URL events.

 The initial drop features 1 random edition from legendary creators and rising stars: Nyan Cat, Reylarsdam, Alberto Rizzo, Thisisarobot, Jimena Buena Vida, Lost Children of Andromeda Echo.gen, Suki Violet and Metamorphic.
